data.description: This Ranch style home is absolutely bright & cheery with some gorgeous original wood work featuring 2 bedrooms on the main floor and a nonconforming bedroom in the basement with new carpeting.  The house showcases lovely hardwood floors on the main level and vinyl planks in the basement's spacious area, which can serve as both a family room and a recreation room.  Newer cedar aligns the ceilings in the living room and dining room to give it that special character.  The garage walks out directly to the fenced backyard, offering ample space for growing vegetables, fruits, or tending to a variety of flowers like roses, daffodils, and tulips. This ensures the home is enveloped in the delightful scents of endless summers and beautiful falls.  New roof in 2017.  Schedule your showings today!!
